react-tipsy Changelog
=====================

Here you can see the full list of changes between each react-tipsy release.

Version 0.6.0
-------------

Released on July 27, 2017

- Fixes #10

Version 0.5.1
-------------

Released on June 14, 2017

- Fixes #8

Version 0.5.0
-------------

Released on May 4, 2017

- Remove deprecated PropTypes, createClass

Version 0.4.3
-------------

Released on May 4, 2017.

- Library name changed to Tipsy as was originally intended to
- Updated README.md to fix documentation inconsistencies

Version 0.4.0
-------------

Released on January 26, 2017.

- Library name changed from "ReactTipsy" to "Tipsy"
- updated package.json to not be reliant on a specific React/ReactDOM version
- updated README.md to fix typos and include props options and methods
- added touch support (ontouchstart and ontouchend events)
- added "manual" trigger
- added new public methods: "toggle", "updatePosition" and "destroy"